# Keep ``apps/web/public/`` in version control even when it's empty.
#
# Next.js scaffolds expect this directory for static assets (favicons,
# OG images, robots.txt). The week-10 build doesn't ship any yet, but
# the Dockerfile's runtime stage ``COPY --from=builder /app/public ./public``
# fails if the directory is missing — and ``next build`` doesn't
# create one for you. The gitkeep is the smallest fix.
